# Time in Kansas

This article needs additional citations for [verification](/Wikipedia:Verifiability). Please help [improve this article](/Special:EditPage/Time_in_Kansas) by [adding citations to reliable sources](/Help:Referencing_for_beginners). Unsourced material may be challenged and removed.
